 中
\begin_inset Formula $\pi^{2}$
\end_inset

组态的
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varSigma$
\end_inset

态的波函数的一个组分
\begin_inset Formula $(1^{\alpha}-1^{\alpha})$
\end_inset

, 即两电子分别占据
\begin_inset Formula $1\pi^{+}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $1\pi^{-}$
\end_inset

两个简并轨道(其中上标
\begin_inset Formula $+$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $-$
\end_inset

分别表示
\begin_inset Formula $m=±1$
\end_inset

), 且自旋都向上。
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varSigma$
\end_inset

态的
\begin_inset Formula $(1^{\alpha}-1^{\alpha})$
\end_inset

组分的波函数
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varPsi(1,2)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
^{3}\varPsi(1,2)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|\begin{array}{cc}
1\pi^{+}\left(1\right)\alpha(1) & 1\pi^{+}\left(2\right)\alpha(2)\\
1\pi^{-}\left(1\right)\alpha(1) & 1\pi^{-}\left(2\right)\alpha(2)
\end{array}\right|\label{eq:3-73}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中令
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left.\begin{split}1\pi^{+} & =A(r,θ)e^{iϕ}\\
1\pi^{-} & =A(r,θ)e^{-iϕ}
\end{split}
\right\} \label{eq:3-74}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
^{3}\varPsi(1,2)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\alpha(1)\alpha(2)A(r_{1},θ_{1})A(r_{2},θ_{2})[e^{iϕ_{1}-iϕ_{2}}-e^{iϕ_{2}-iϕ_{1}}]
\]

\end_inset

经
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{xz}$
\end_inset

平面的反映, 可用反映操作算符
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\sigma}_{xz}$
\end_inset

作用于
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varPsi(1,2)$
\end_inset

表示。于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\sigma}_{xz}^{3}\varPsi(1,2)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\alpha(1)\alpha(2)A(r_{1},θ_{1})A(r_{2},θ_{2})[e^{-iϕ_{1}+iϕ_{2}}-e^{-iϕ_{2}+iϕ_{1}}]=-^{3}\varPsi(1,2)\label{eq:3-75}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varPsi(1,2)$
\end_inset

对平面反映是反对称的。同样可以检验
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varSigma$
\end_inset

其它两个波函数组分对平面
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{xz}$
\end_inset

反映也是反对称的, 所以把这种状态记为
\begin_inset Formula $^{3}\varSigma^{-}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\varSigma$
\end_inset

态的波函数
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\varPsi(1,2)$
\end_inset

为两个Slater行列式的线性组合
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{multline}
^{1}\varPsi(1,2)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|\begin{array}{cc}
1\pi^{+}\left(1\right)\alpha(1) & 1\pi^{+}\left(2\right)\alpha(2)\\
1\pi^{-}\left(1\right)\beta(1) & 1\pi^{-}\left(2\right)\beta(2)
\end{array}\right|-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|\begin{array}{cc}
1\pi^{+}\left(1\right)\beta(1) & 1\pi^{+}\left(2\right)\beta(2)\\
1\pi^{-}\left(1\right)\alpha(1) & 1\pi^{-}\left(2\right)\alpha(2)
\end{array}\right|\\
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}[\alpha(1)\beta(2)-\beta(1)\alpha(2)]A(r_{1},θ_{1})A(r_{2},θ_{2})[e^{i(ϕ_{1}-ϕ_{2})}+e^{i(ϕ_{2}-ϕ_{1})}]\label{eq:3-76}
\end{multline}

\end_inset

显然
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\sigma}_{xz}^{1}\varPsi(1,2)=^{1}\varPsi(1,2)\label{eq:3-77}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

 即
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\varSigma$
\end_inset

态是对称的, 记为
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\varSigma^{+}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $^{1}\varDelta$
\end_inset

态是简并的, 接表 
