\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\ce{H2}$
\end_inset

分子的Hamilton算符为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}=-\frac{1}{2}\nabla_{1}^{2}-\frac{1}{2}\nabla_{2}^{2}-\frac{1}{r_{a1}}-\frac{1}{r_{b2}}-\frac{1}{r_{a2}}-\frac{1}{r_{b1}}+\frac{1}{r_{12}}+\frac{1}{R}\label{eq:3-85}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中1和2表示两个电子, 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

表示两个原子核(见图 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:3-19"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)。令
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\hat{h}_{a}(1) & =-\frac{1}{2}\nabla_{1}^{2}-\frac{1}{r_{a1}}\label{eq:3-86}\\
\hat{h}_{b}(2) & =-\frac{1}{2}\nabla_{2}^{2}-\frac{1}{r_{b2}}\label{eq:3-87}\\
V(1,2) & =-\frac{1}{r_{a2}}-\frac{1}{r_{b1}}+\frac{1}{r_{12}}+\frac{1}{R}\label{eq:3-88}
\end{align}

\end_inset

得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}=\hat{h}_{a}(1)+\hat{h}_{b}(2)+V(1,2)\label{eq:3-89}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\hat{h}_{a}(1)$
\end_inset

是原子
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

的电子1的Hamilton算符, 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{h}_{b}(2)$
\end_inset

是原子
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

的电子2的Hamilton算符, 
\begin_inset Formula $V(1,2)$
\end_inset

是两个原子间的相互作用能算符。
\begin_inset Formula $\ce{H2}$
\end_inset

的Schr
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

{o}
\end_layout

\end_inset

dinger方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}\varPsi(1,2)=E\varPsi(1,2)\label{eq:3-90}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设两个氢原子的电子都处于基态, 则两个电子的波函数分别为
\begin_inset Formula $1s_{a}(1)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $1s_{b}(2)$
\end_inset

, 因为电子是不可区分的, 所以基态的两个电子波函数也可以分别是
\begin_inset Formula $1s_{a}(2)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $1s_{b}(1)$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $\ce{H2}$
\end_inset

的两个电子的波函数可写成如下形式: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\varPsi(1,2)=c_{1}1s_{a}(1)1s_{b}(2)+c_{2}1s_{a}(2)1s_{b}(1)\label{eq:3-91}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

即采用一对电子的波函数的线性组合来表示两个电子的总波函数。把上式代入到(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3-90"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式, 利用线性变分法可解出
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
E_{S} & =2\epsilon+\frac{Q+A}{1+S^{2}}\label{eq:3-92}\\
\varPsi_{S}(1,2) & =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2+2S^{2}}}[1s_{a}(1)1s_{b}(2)+1s_{a}(2)1s_{b}(1)]\label{eq:3-93}\\
E_{A} & =2\epsilon+\frac{Q-A}{1-S^{2}}\label{eq:3-94}\\
\varPsi_{A}(1,2) & =\frac{1}{\sqrt{2-2S^{2}}}[1s_{a}(1)1s_{b}(2)-1s_{a}(2)1s_{b}(1)]\label{eq:3-95}
\end{align}

\end_inset

式中
